OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,FFrom tomorrow, bus replacement
OL,7,Fservices will operate between
OL,8,FTweedbank and Edinburgh for the next
OL,9,Fthree Sundays.
OL,11,FNetwork Rail have said that it has
OL,12,Fscheduled weekend closures for the
OL,13,Frest of March to begin work to
OL,14,Felectrify the line - which when
OL,15,Fcomplete, will cut carbon emissions,
OL,16,Freduce operating costs, and enhance
OL,17,Fthe overall passenger experience.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
