OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,FDuring this time, engineers will be
OL,7,Fputting in the infrastructure which
OL,8,Fwill carry the overhead line equipment
OL,9,Fand eventually enable electric trains
OL,10,Fto run on the Borders Railway.
OL,12,FThe nature of the work means it can
OL,13,Fonly be carried out safely when trains
OL,14,Faren't running. Part of the work will
OL,15,Falso be carried out overnight to make
OL,16,Fthe best use of the time when the line
OL,17,Fis closed.
OL,19,FTrains will still be running between
OL,20,FNewcraighall and Edinburgh Waverley.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,FPassengers are advised to plan ahead,
OL,7,Fcheck their journeys with ScotRail
OL,8,Fbefore travelling, and allow extra
OL,9,Ftime where needed.
OL,11,FWhen will services be affected:
OL,12,FSaturday 14th - Monday 16th March
OL,13,FSaturday 21st - Monday 23th March
OL,14,FSaturday 28th - Monday 30th March
OL,16,FThe work follows the Scottish
OL,17,FGovernment's announcement in September
OL,18,Flast year of a #342m investment to
OL,19,Felectrify routes in Fife and the
OL,20,FBorders and introduce new
OL,21,Fbatteryelectric trains.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,F"The Borders Railway was rebuilt with
OL,7,Ffuture electrification in mind," said
OL,8,FLynsey Maclean, scheme project manager
OL,9,Fat Network Rail Scotland.
OL,11,F"Which means we can deliver this work
OL,12,Fwith far less intrusive engineering
OL,13,Fthan is required on many older parts
OL,14,Fof the network, where we often need to
OL,15,Flower track or raise bridges. The
OL,16,Finfrastructure here is already
OL,17,Fsuitable for this next stage of
OL,18,Fmodernisation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,F"Piling is still a vital early step in
OL,7,Finstalling the overhead line equipment
OL,8,Fthat will eventually power electric
OL,9,Ftrains. Our teams have planned the
OL,10,Factivity carefully to keep disruption
OL,11,Fto a minimum for passengers and those
OL,12,Fliving near the railway.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
