OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,F"We're grateful to customers and local
OL,7,Fresidents for their patience while we
OL,8,Fcomplete this phase of the project.
OL,9,FElectrification will deliver longterm
OL,10,Fbenefits for the Borders, and this
OL,11,Fwork marks an important milestone in
OL,12,Fcreating a cleaner, more reliable and
OL,13,Fmore sustainable railway for the
OL,14,Ffuture."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
