OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,FMark Ilderton, ScotRail Service
OL,7,FDelivery Director, said: "The
OL,8,Felectrification of sections of Borders
OL,9,FRailway is an important step in paving
OL,10,Fthe way for new, greener trains and
OL,11,Fdelivering a more modern railway for
OL,12,Fthe communities we serve.
OL,14,F"These early works mark real progress
OL,15,Ftowards introducing new trains, which
OL,16,Fwill offer customers a quieter,
OL,17,Fsmoother, and more environmentally
OL,18,Fsustainable journeys along the route.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773529871
OL,3,CDisruption to Borders Railway services
OL,4,Cas work to electrify line begins
OL,6,F"We know that electrification works
OL,7,Fcan cause inconvenience to customers,
OL,8,Fso we're working closely with Network
OL,9,FRail to keep customers informed and
OL,10,Fwill provide clear alternative travel
OL,11,Farrangements so customers can continue
OL,12,Fto travel with confidence when the
OL,13,Fproject is underway."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@UO]
